{"tid":1274722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個發夢、散步時，被關心同支持嘅經歷。","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T18:14:46.000Z","uid":253438,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b571855eb80fa3e0dec8ca3cb8fdec17409b3a0","tid":1274722,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不如大家一齊回想下，<br />\n分享呢個月有乜嘢令你感到被關心被支持，<br />\n可能係說話，可能係行動，<br />\n可能係你好親嘅人，亦都可能係陌生人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一齊用自己嘅經歷，<br />\n鼓勵每一位辛苦嘅巴絲。</span><br />\n<br />\n愛每一位愛香港嘅香港人!</span>"},{"pid":"dc373f5bad1ede013002458d3d5dac8e1ee913f2","tid":1274722,"uid":253438,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"我就搵到一個理念相近，有默契，互相照顧到嘅同伴！<br />\n關心得來又會講吓笑。<br />\n又可以一齊分析形勢。"},{"pid":"ca061a6a040f2bca16056255c13475780d14a08e","tid":1274722,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n比正能量所有巴絲"},{"pid":"4e54c12fd09d5a5065db66100faa7267aedc87d2","tid":1274722,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"646629e82111d78819b89a647eaace80746d610f","tid":1274722,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"a98311d94a994b6d62860b982ddc0576ee8847ac","tid":1274722,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ee5030a22065897cd8f661f94fbc59c27f674354","tid":1274722,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"600eb416cc397dd75ca96423c1c8bfdde3831ad1","tid":1274722,"uid":61830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa84b8b96cc1baf9623fdc73e4729ecb